metadata.name: Rice Courier Campfire
metadata.description:
In reality, everyone needs a break, even those of us who thrive on being busy and love what we do!

the same thing for our Rice Courier, they were chosen by the universe itself, to spread the magic of rice and its powers to all the corners of the universe.

be it day or night, a beach or the moon, among the poor, rich, hungry, or sick. 

There is plenty of rice to go around for any. 
There is plenty of rice to heal the world.

All with the power of the rice.
